            "name": "Narrow Lore",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Monomania",
        "subtype": "ability",
        "text": "Each obsessive researcher is preoccupied with a hyper-specialized, niche body of knowledge (their Narrow Lore) in which they are the acknowledged world authority. The catch is that when such an expert goes wrong, they go badly wrong\u2014 if an obsessive researcher gets a success on a Narrow Lore roll, they get a critical success instead. But if they roll a failure, then they get a critical failure instead.",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
      },
      {
        "ability_type": "interaction",
        "name": "World-Class Authority",
        "subtype": "ability",
        "text": "In their narrow field of interest, the obsessive researcher is a 10th-level challenge.",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
      }
    ],
